snippet.title: Of Blades & Tails - Early Access October 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
Of Blades & Tails, our upcoming turn-based pixel-art action RPG roguelite, will have it's Steam Early Access launch on October 19th 2022!

Wishlist and follow now! Check out the free demo!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1768780/Of_Blades__Tails/
